  <brief_title>Myeloid-Related Protein in Evaluation of Acute Chest Pain in the Emergency Departement</brief_title>
  <acronym>MyRiAD</acronym>
  <official_title>Study of Myeloid-related Protein 8/14 and Additional Biomarkers (Multi Marker Approach) for Early Diagnosis and Risk Stratification in Patients Presenting With Acute Chest Pain at the Emergency Department</official_title>
